{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Limit Repeat Abortions",
        "additional_details": "This petition calls for compassionate regulations to limit repeat abortions, while fully protecting access in cases of rape, abuse, coercion, or serious risk to the woman\u2019s or baby\u2019s health. In our view abortion should not be used as a substitute for contraception. We believe greater safeguards, education, and access to effective contraception are needed to support women, reduce repeat procedures, and protect life through responsible, trauma-informed care.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to set a limit on the number of abortions someone can have, except in cases of abuse, rape or medical need.",
